OL,3,CTributes paid to 30-year-old who
OL,4,C'brought joy, happiness and laughter'
OL,6,FThe family of a 30-year-old who died
OL,7,Fafter being stabbed in east Bristol
OL,8,Fhave paid tribute to him as a man who
OL,9,F"brought joy, happiness, laughter and
OL,10,Fprotection".
OL,12,FAliki Mamwa, known as Alex, died in
OL,13,Fhospital on Tuesday 5 March, following
OL,14,Fof St Pauls.
OL,16,FA 43-year-old has been charged with
OL,17,Fhis murder.
