OL,6,FIn a tribute released on Friday 15
OL,7,FMarch, Alex's family said: "Alex
OL,8,Fbrought joy, happiness, laughter and
OL,9,Fprotection to all those he loved and
OL,10,Fthose who met him. His presence and
OL,11,Fsmile always lit up a room.
OL,13,F"Alex was not troublesome, he kept
OL,14,Fhimself to himself and was always very
OL,15,Fhumble.
