OL,3,CTributes paid to 30-year-old who
OL,4,C'brought joy, happiness and laughter'
OL,6,F"Alex was looking forward to
OL,7,Ffulfilling many of his life plans,
OL,8,Funfortunately this was cut short
OL,9,Fmercilessly. He did not deserve for
OL,10,Fhis life to be taken in such a tragic
OL,11,Fway and at such a young age.
OL,13,F"We, his family are devastated and we
OL,14,Fwill truly miss him. As time passes
OL,15,Fand fades away, our memories and love
OL,16,Ffor him will always stay.
OL,18,F"The only thing we ask for is that
OL,19,Fjustice be served in Alex's favour."
