OL,6,FAlex's family are being supported by
OL,7,Fspecially-trained liaison officers
OL,8,Ffrom Avon and Somerset Police.
OL,10,FDavid Malcolm, of St Marks Road in
OL,11,FEaston, appeared at Bristol Crown
OL,12,FCourt on 11 March charged with Alex's
OL,13,Fmurder. He has been ahead of a seven-
OL,14,Fday trial, which is scheduled to begin
OL,15,Fon 19 August.
